) species and hybrids (
<emphasis box="[536,555,405,428]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="107">P.</emphasis>
x 
<emphasis box="[585,703,404,428]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="107">jablokowii</emphasis>
